flowchart TD
    START([Start])
    A[Ballot Summary section updates]
    B[Click: Cast 7 Votes button]
    C[Confirmation modal opens]
    D[Review all selections]
    E[Click: Confirm & Submit]
    F[MetaMask transaction popup appears]
    G[User clicks Confirm in MetaMask]
    H{Transaction mined on blockchain?}
    I[Green toast: Vote recorded successfully]
    J[Red toast: Transaction failed]
    K[Contract emits BallotCast event]
    L[Sync engine increments vote count in DB]
    M[Live results updated via Socket.IO]
    START --> A --> B --> C --> D --> E --> F --> G --> H
    H -->|Success| I --> K --> L --> M --> END([End])
    H -->|Failed| J --> END
